cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this project, please cite the underlying One-Step Image Translation paper and this repository."
title: "GPA: GAN-made Pixel-Art Translation Using Deep-Learning Techniques"
authors:
  - family-names: "İşmen"
    given-names: "Kaan Ümit"
