abstract: >-
  A single-step, unpaired image-to-image translation system that converts real
  photographs into pixel-art, built on CycleGAN-Turbo (img2img-turbo) and extended
  with a differentiable palette loss. Özyeğin University CS402 Senior Project, 2025.
date-released: 2025-06-01
